        <abstract> 
<p>Returns two volumes of <hi rend="italic">Felix Holt</hi> [George Eliot (1866)]</p> 
            <p>and the Coddington [lens].</p> 
<p>John Smith will send <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>.</p>  
<p><hi rend="italic">Nation</hi> reports that Louis Agassiz holds that the Amazon Valley was formed since the glacial epoch.</p> 
